201
00:17:03,926 --> 00:17:05,835
No mínimo.

202
00:17:05,886 --> 00:17:07,879
São 500 mil no teu bolso.

203
00:17:10,183 --> 00:17:13,184
Esquece o passado, Tobey.

204
00:17:14,270 --> 00:17:16,310
Ficou para trás.

205
00:17:17,523 --> 00:17:20,524
Vim para fazer as pazes.

206
00:17:20,610 --> 00:17:22,686
E dinheiro.

207
00:17:24,656 --> 00:17:25,854
Não respondas agora.

208
00:17:26,741 --> 00:17:28,817
Pensa nisso.

209
00:17:30,995 --> 00:17:33,118
Não preciso de pensar.

210
00:17:35,208 --> 00:17:37,248
Eu aceito.

211
00:17:38,169 --> 00:17:40,458
Vou trazer o carro amanhã.

212
00:17:55,020 --> 00:17:59,018
Eu queria tomar a iniciativa
e perguntar...

213
00:17:59,149 --> 00:18:01,272
